"550","<P STYLE=font: 11pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif; margin: 0; text-align: justify>Our consideration of the Fund&rsquo;s"
"551","internal control over financial reporting was for the limited purpose described in the first paragraph and would not necessarily"
"552","disclose all deficiencies in internal control over financial reporting that might be material weaknesses under standards established"
"553","by the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States). However, we noted no deficiencies in the Fund&rsquo;s internal"
"554","control over financial reporting and its operation, including controls over safeguarding securities that we consider to be material"
"555","weaknesses as defined above as of June&nbsp;30, 2019.</P>"
